T1  - Partnership Formation: The Role of Social Status
AU  - Bhattacharya, Haimanti
AU  - Dugar, Subhasish
Y1  - 2014/01/17
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2013.1818
